{"word":"Macedonia","slug":"macedonia","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Macedonia</b> A country in southeastern Europe.<br/> Paul has a vision concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=9'>Act 16:9</a><br/> Paul preaches in, at Philippi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=12'>Act 16:12</a><br/> Paul revisits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=6'>Act 20:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=2&verse=13'>2Co 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=7&verse=5'>2Co 7:5</a><br/> Church at, sends contributions to the poor in Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=15&verse=26'>Rom 15:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=5'>2Co 8:5</a><br/> Timothy visits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=22'>Act 19:22</a><br/> Disciples in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=23'>Act 19:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=2'>Act 27:2</a>"}]}